  <?dbhtml filename="xkbcomp.html"?>

  <title>xkbcomp-&xkbcomp-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      xkbcomp is a tool to compile XKB definitions into map files the server can
      use.
    </para>

